relation: The process whose specific outcome is the progression of the slug over time, from its formation to the mature structure. The process whose specific outcome is the progression of the slug over time, from its formation to the mature structure. Slug development takes place during fruiting body development in cellular slime molds. The slug is the migratory structure formed when the finger bends from a vertical position to a horizontal position.
